Lots of love to a classic war horse...Mosin NagantI have put many, many hours in making this a great sporterized Mosin. It is wearing a Monte Carlo Synthetic Stock with their bolt conversion for scope clearance. I Tweaked the trigger for a more crisp break. Polished everything around the action so it is smooth.
